test_all_negative_one_range:
assert [-1, -1, -1] == []
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: -1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [-1, -1, -1]
test_list_of_even_numbers:
assert [-30, -50, -70] == [-40, -50, -60, -70, -80]
  At index 0 diff: -30 != -40
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: -70
  Full diff:
  - [-40, -50, -60, -70, -80]
  + [-30, -50, -70]
test_negative_odd_range:
assert [-5, -9, -13] == []
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: -5
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [-5, -9, -13]
